\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 She'd be more productive with a needle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Yes. I think the country people didn't read so much in those days did they, no. No.
