\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Do you remember any funerals in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4141808\charrsid3473785 fa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 mily before 1918?
