\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4141808\charrsid3473785 C}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 ould you describe a funeral in those days, who attended?
