Yes. Yes, very deep mourning. Yes. The first - funeral I do remember was my grandmother and they had black crepe then, don't suppose you've heard of that have you? She wore 
a little cape with deep black crape right round and round the skirt. Of course that was - used for mourning in those days.
\par 
