\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 They didn't say you mustn't play with certain children because they were rough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 No, I only saw them from the window. I never went out to play with them. If I went out I went out with me mother or m
e father or me brothers you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
