\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 What organisations were these?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Well - the - of course there was Sunday school c
lass and - the different - if - as I got older we went to classes you see. To different - so far back - yes - the girls -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Were they Bible classes and this sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Yes, there were Bible classes, yes. And there were classes that we could go
 to you see to - to read or - some of them used to play - like table tennis, not that, but that kind of thing you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Games evenings?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Like social evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Yes, that's right. Not for very long though.
