Yes, we used to - not mine - the boys used to have - pigeons and fly pigeons and - of course - we had the cat and dog. If I went out I nearly always had the dog. Yes. But - they used to swim and - play cricket - of course I wasn't in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Did you used to go swimming or fishing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 No. I never went - no, couldn't go - couldn't play cricket and I didn't go swimming No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 How about cycling or anything like that?
