\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 This is after you'd le}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12543445\charrsid3473785 f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
