\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 But until you le}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12543445\charrsid3473785 f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 t school you pretty well kept to your home?
