e uncle that was on the Titanic, I told you yes. That's how far back it would be you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Did your parents give you any pocket money?
