 some things you do whereas some when I was home I wasn't much - of course - yes, of course there's fun going on all the time and we had our - we had tea there always. Not {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}
{\xmlattrvalue 0}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 12}}}mi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2504814\charrsid3473785 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 day{\*\xmlclose}
 meal but teatime, had a tea and that was fun there you know, among the girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 More of a place to meet people in a way was it?
