I met her when - she was a new girl you see - I had started there, she was a new girl so she - asked me several things you see and I helped her and - and - then when she came to do the wo
rk well we worked together you see. Then we used to go home - well no, I didn't go home with her because she lived in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Kent{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} in that direction.

