Well no, just this one. I knew others but we weren't very intimate, it was just her and I went everywhere and - there was a - a lady lives in this street too that worked the same, she said - I hadn't seen her for yea}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2504814\charrsid3473785 rs and she said to me - you're J}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 anet aren't you? I said, no, I'm not I'm Julia. And we were always together, she didn't know which was Janet and which was Julia.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Did you still have to be home by a certain time in the evenings?
