\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Did she expect to know where you were when you went out?
