you see. You must - of course you must stop them from doing wrong but - they go their own way and they will have that way if they possibly can, they like their own way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Were there any ideas of binging up children at this time which you strongly disagreed with or any ideas you felt very strongly about?
