I don't know. I don't know of any. I didn't let them run outside you see, because of the traffic for one thing, but they - children do run out and they are just coming home from school you see. Well
 they went to - they went to school themselves, when they were old enough - and - came home alone but - I was always somewhere -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 You'd give them a little bit of independence?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15862227 JG  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Yes. Yes, that's right. To see they were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Did you and your husband have the same ideas about bringing up children?
