 - from then I thought she must have been. But - there was another girl after her - after she died and mother - this person said, oh would you come in Mrs Curry and have a look at my Beattie. So mother said, yes, well I'll come in any time. She would have
 to the other little girl if she'd been asked you see. And she want in and - well she grew a bonny girl. Yes. I can't remember - I know it was Beattie but that little - beautiful little girl.
