ents. They were very fond of him and he was of them you see. And he used to have a lot more toys tha}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11419800\charrsid3473785 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 
 the other two, 'cos grand - grandparents would buy things for him but - they got on all right.
