emed to - do the right thing. Yes. Took it in their stride as it were, they were - nice children, they were. That ; that little boy, the one - was killed - he was - he was a nice boy, exceptionally nice. He used to say - sometimes when I've been up very e
arly, I'd sit in the chair and nearly go to sleep and they were playing. Sssh. Mum's gone to sleep. I could hear.
