Yes. Well - I always liked them to keep tidy when they went to school and - and do what they were told, they did too, they were good boys so the master told me. And - yes at that - that was one in the Air}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11419800\charrsid3473785  F}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 
orce, Douglas, he was exceptional at school more than - so was Geoffrey, he was very good at school you know. But the elder boy didn't matter - he didn't - he never bothered, didn't matter.
