Not a bit, not. When he brought home a report from school, there's my report mum. Oh, I said, you haven't done so and so. It doesn't matter, mum, doesn't matter. All right. It didn't, nothing mattered. But - he went to - he worked at th
e - Post Office - what do you call it, he was on the phone -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16009757 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid138725\charrsid3473785 Telephonist?
